ian Hochhauser *2010 - Rachel Cameron *2011 - [[Monica Mason]] *2012 - [[Antoinette Sibley]] *2014 - [[The Royal Ballet]] *2016 - [[Matthew Bourne]]<ref name=bourne>{{cite web|title=Matthew Bourne honoured for services to ballet {{!}} News {{!}} The Stage|url=https://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2016/matthew-bourne-honoured-for-his-services-to-ballet/|website=The Stage|accessdate=30 July 2017|date=24 June 2016}}</ref> *2018 - [[Carlos Acosta]]
